text: Carlos Alberto Vario (born 17 October 1947) is an Argentine wrestler. He competed at the 1964 Summer Olympics and the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1947 births Category:Living people Category:Argentine male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Argentina Category:Wrestlers at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Buenos Aires
